ing nothing&quot; and just chilling. <br /><br />I also know that if I start buffin you, other nearby players may well get the idea they can ask. I will oblige them too.. but in the long run, your simply request does have a larger effect. Its up to me to manage this, I agree, but its not as simple as just &quot;spreading the light&quot;. <br /><br />Still, I agree that cooperation and encouragement are what makes this game great, and its great to help others meet their goals!</p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />Hack that mob to bits.. get it down to ones and zeros fast!</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td></tr></table>
